          "audioFile": "chrono_match_start_bebop_chrono_convo03_01",
          "audioUrl": "audio/chrono_match_start_bebop_chrono_convo03_01.mp3",
          "text": "Bebop\u2026 that\u2019s a curious name for a golem",
          "duration": 3.806
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "character": "Bebop",
          "audioFile": "bebop_match_start_bebop_chrono_convo03_02",
          "audioUrl": "audio/bebop_match_start_bebop_chrono_convo03_02.mp3",
          "text": "Ms shelly's a fan of music.",
          "duration": 2.255
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "character": "Paradox",
          "audioFile": "chrono_match_start_bebop_chrono_convo03_03",
          "audioUrl": "audio/chrono_match_start_bebop_chrono_convo03_03.mp3",
          "text": "Do you play?",
          "duration": 1.116
        },
        {
          "order": 4,
          "character": "Bebop",
          "audioFile": "bebop_match_start_bebop_chrono_convo03_04",
          "audioUrl": "audio/bebop_match_start_bebop_chrono_convo03_04.mp3",
          "text": "Sadly no, these hands aren't exactly delicate.",
          "duration": 3.87
        },
        {
          "order": 5,
          "character": "Paradox",
          "audioFile": "chrono_match_start_bebop_chrono_convo03_05",
          "audioUrl": "audio/chrono_match_start_bebop_chrono_convo03_05.mp3",
          "text": "You gonna let a little thing like hands stop you?",
          "duration": 2.863
        },
        {
          "order": 6,
          "character": "Bebop",
          "audioFile": "bebop_match_start_bebop_chrono_convo03_06",
          "audioUrl": "audio/bebop_match_start_bebop_chrono_convo03_06.mp3",
          "text": "It seems rather important.",
          "duration": 2.102
        },
        {
          "order": 7,
          "character": "Paradox",
          "audioFile": "chrono_match_start_bebop_chrono_convo03_07",
          "audioUrl": "audio/chrono_match_start_bebop_chrono_convo03_07.mp3",
          "text": "Suppose so, but I bet there's a solution if you try hard enough",
          "duration": 4.56
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "conversationId": "bebop_dynamo_convo01",
      "lines": [
        {
          "order": 1,
          "character": "Bebop",
          "audioFile": "bebop_match_start_bebop_dynamo_convo01_01",
          "audioUrl": "audio/bebop_match_start_bebop_dynamo_convo01_01.mp3",
          "text": "So who made you?",
          "duration": 1.281
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "character": "Dynamo",
          "audioFile": "dynamo_match_start_bebop_dynamo_convo01_02",
          "audioUrl": "audio/dynamo_match_start_bebop_dynamo_convo01_02.mp3",
          "text": "Oh, I wasn't made - my body just was obliterataed by an astral gate.",
          "duration": 3.544
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "character": "Bebop",
          "audioFile": "bebop_match_start_bebop_dynamo_convo01_03",
          "audioUrl": "audio/bebop_match_start_bebop_dynamo_convo01_03.mp3",
          "text": "Shame, thought I found a kindred spirit.",
